    "In this layer, all the input units have a separable weight to each output unit.",
    "There are two of fully connected layer one is for input and other is for output.",
    "The fully connected input layer flattens the input and change it into the vector for the input of next stage.",
    "Then the next stage analyzes it and apply weight to project the right label.",
    "Then the fully connected output provides the expected labels to each label [80]."
